---

<section id="how-we-work" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-slide-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">
        Tu proceso legal
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Paso 1 -->
      <div class="step-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Hablamos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Cuéntanos tu situación. Nosotros evaluamos tu caso y te explicamos qué haremos, cuánto cuesta y cuánto tarda. Sin compromiso.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Gratis y sin compromiso</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 2 -->
      <div class="step-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Preparamos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Te decimos qué documentos necesitas. Tú los envías. Nosotros nos encargamos de traducciones, apostillas y legalizaciones.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Lista clara de documentos</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 3 -->
      <div class="step-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Representamos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Firmas un poder notarial en tu país. Nosotros actuamos por ti ante notarios, Hacienda y registros. Sin viajar a España.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Todo desde tu país</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 4 -->
      <div class="step-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Gestionamos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Hacemos todos los trámites: presentamos documentos, pagamos impuestos, seguimos el proceso hasta que todo esté resuelto.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Nosotros lo hacemos todo</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 5 -->
      <div class="step-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">5</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Te informamos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Te contamos cómo va todo. Respondemos tus dudas en español, inglés o noruego. Te enviamos actualizaciones cuando hay novedades.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>En tu idioma</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 6 -->
      <div class="step-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">6</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Entregamos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Te enviamos todos los documentos finales. Te explicamos qué hacer después. Y seguimos disponibles si necesitas algo más.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Todo resuelto</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-primary/5 border-l-4 border-primary p-8 rounded-r-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">
          Escribenos hoy
        </h3>
        <a 
          href="https://cloud-s23.mnprogram.net/Index.aspx?frm=DAF6F06B-7DA0-49A9-B613-887B49F5B84B" 
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
        >
          Contactar Ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .step-card {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
</style>

